    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to accept because people always want to tell you \"it gets better\" or \"make an impact,\" but they're lying, right? if the end result is always nothingness, then all the effort of living, the pain, the sadness... it's all just extra weight for no reason. it feels more like a burden than a gift. like, why stay in a burning building if you know it's going to collapse anyway?",
